statements.sql: select `workspaces`.*, `user_workspaces`.`permission` from `workspaces` inner join `user_workspaces` on `workspaces`.`id` = `user_workspaces`.`workspace_id` where `workspaces`.`id` = 4 and `user_id` = 7 limit 1

select * from `ch_messages` inner join `users` on `ch_messages`.`from_id` = `users`.`id` or `ch_messages`.`to_id` = `users`.`id` where `ch_messages`.`workspace_id` = 4 and (`ch_messages`.`from_id` = 7 or `ch_messages`.`to_id` = 7) order by `ch_messages`.`created_at` desc

select `users`.*, `user_workspaces`.`permission`, `user_workspaces`.`is_active` from `users` inner join `user_workspaces` on `user_workspaces`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` where `user_workspaces`.`workspace_id` = 4 and `users`.`id` != 7
